		<h3 align="center">About</h3><br />
		<p>This billing system accepts 2 payment methods from its customers. Customers can be billed online using a credit card, or they may use their remaining credits which can be acquired by buying it from the merchant's office. </p>
		<p>In order to accept online payments from customer's bank accounts, this system uses 2checkout's payment processing service so customer's can pay by using their credit cards. 2checkout accepts payment from most of the major credit cards interationally, which includes Visa, Mastercard, American Express, Discover, Dinners Club, and JCB. To see the complete details, you may visit <a href="http://www.siteground.com/merchant_2checkout.htm">http://www.siteground.com/merchant_2checkout.htm</a></p>
		<p>Customers can also be billed using their remaining credits in the website. If a customer is already a member, he / she may purchase additional credits from the merchant's office and use these credits to purchase products or services online with just a few simple clicking in your personal computer. </p>
