		<h3 align="center">How to order</h3>
		<p>If you already have your own account, just log in and you will be directed already in the Store page. You'll have the option to select the products or services you wish to purchase. Just type in the quantity of the product / service you wish to purchase and add them in your virtual cart. After selecting all the products, select one of the 2 payment methods available by clicking the corresponding button below your cart's view.</p>
		<p>If ever you chose to pay using your credit card, you will be redirected to an external website in http://www.2checkout.com. From there, you'll have to enter your credit card information, address and other informations required in order to process your credit card transaction. Once finished, you will receive an email notification confirming your purchase, which you may also print as a receipt for future reference. Click on the "return" button to go back to this website so that we'll also be informed immediately about your purchase. Don't worry if your forgot to click that "return" button from 2checkout because we have different sources from getting that info.</p>
